title: Electric company tv soundtrack 1972
description:
If u grew up watching Pbs in the 70s you watched the Electric company tv series.
Morgan Freeman,Rita Mariano,Bill Cosby and others were the main stars on this series.
Irene Cara was a member of the Short circus.
Now heres the 1972 original LP On Warner bros records.Sourced from my original vinyl LP in flac since it has never been released on cd yet.
